      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Necromancy</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nYou shoot a greenish ray at a creature within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 Poison damage and has the Poisoned|XPHB condition until the end of your next turn.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 2d8|1-9|1d8 for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
